# Live camera (confirmed working)

The Birdhouse live feed works end-to-end. Do not "simplify" back to a direct browser→Railway HLS URL — that fails in the browser due to CORS + Basic auth against MediaMTX.

## Architecture

- Wyze Cam → Railway `wyze-bridge` (image `mrlt8/wyze-bridge`)
- Public domain targets port **8888** (HLS). Port **5000** is WebUI only. Port **8554** RTSP stays private.
- Next.js proxies HLS at `src/app/api/camera/[...path]/route.ts`
- Player uses same-origin URL: `/api/camera/bird/stream.m3u8`

## Required env (`.env.local` / Vercel)

```bash
NEXT_PUBLIC_CAMERA_PROTOCOL=hls
NEXT_PUBLIC_CAMERA_STREAM_URL=/api/camera/bird/stream.m3u8

CAMERA_UPSTREAM_BASE=https://wyze-bridge-production.up.railway.app
CAMERA_STREAM_USER=wb
CAMERA_STREAM_PASSWORD=<WB_API from bridge WebUI — not the Wyze developer API_KEY>
```

**Confirmed working** on local `npm run dev` and on Vercel production (after those env vars + redeploy).

### On-demand Railway (cost control, faster wake)

Bridge starts when the user taps Live Cam (pre-warm on press) and stops after `CAMERA_IDLE_MINUTES` (cron `/api/bridge/idle-check`).

Speed levers (cannot be instant from a full stop):
1. Pre-warm on tap/hover before `/live-camera` mounts
2. `serviceInstanceRedeploy` of existing image — no rebuild
3. Keep-alive window so re-opens within ~12 min are instant
4. Never restart a healthy SUCCESS deploy just to “wake”

Env: `RAILWAY_API_TOKEN`, `RAILWAY_SERVICE_ID`, `RAILWAY_ENVIRONMENT_ID`, optional `CAMERA_IDLE_MINUTES`, `CRON_SECRET`

Railway wyze-bridge must stay Running with the public domain on port 8888 while viewing.

Camera path is `bird` (Wyze name "Bird"). Auth user for streams is `wb`.

Diagnostics: `/api/camera-status`, `/api/bridge/status`, `/api/camera/bird/stream.m3u8` (should start with `#EXTM3U`).

Wyze developer `API_ID` / `API_KEY` are Railway-only for the bridge; never `NEXT_PUBLIC_*`.

## Code touchpoints

- `src/lib/camera/*` — HLS player; always-mounted `<video>` for attach
- `src/app/api/camera/[...path]/route.ts` — server-side Basic auth + upstream fetch
- `src/lib/railway/wyzeBridge.ts` + `/api/bridge/*` — on-demand start/stop
- **Stream only on `/live-camera`** — home `LiveCameraCard` is a static poster + link; it must never mount `CameraPlayer` / open HLS
- Pre-warm via `prewarmCameraBridge()` on Live Cam press
